THE PLAN'S SECOND STAGE.

481
00:24:14,921 --> 00:24:17,658
[AKATSUKI, VOICE‐OVER]
MICHITAKA OF THE MARINE AGENCY.

482
00:24:17,758 --> 00:24:19,893
KARASHIN OF SHOPPING STREET 8.

483
00:24:19,993 --> 00:24:21,928
RODERICK OF THE RODERICK
MERCHANT GUILD.

484
00:24:22,028 --> 00:24:25,866
MASTERS OF THE LARGEST CRAFTING
GUILDS GATHER INTO ONE PLACE.

485
00:24:25,966 --> 00:24:28,101
THEIR TRADING PARTNERS
ARE THE CRESCENT MOONS,

486
00:24:28,201 --> 00:24:29,770
MARIELLE AND HENRIETTA.

487
00:24:29,870 --> 00:24:32,739
